rComments: Horrible prof, totally incomprehensible, also doesn't communicate requirements until the very last moment. I was lucky that I was bilingual and able to understand his half translated slides and rambles. if you're forced to take a class with him, wait until next year (2011) when the other profs teaching the courses return. Not worth it.
Si vous pouvez prendre le cours avec un autre prof, faites-le. Il pense qu'il sait tout et tanne tout le monde avec son arrogance. Examens bâtards. Cours bâtard. Prof bâtard !
